      "value": "A grand banquet hall scene rendered in the style of a 16th-century Flemish oil painting, but the guest of honor is a modern astronaut in a bulky white NASA spacesuit seated at the head of a long oak table. The astronaut's gold-visored helmet reflects the candlelight as it reaches with a thick gloved hand for a roasted turkey leg. Around it, peasants and nobles in period velvet and lace raise pewter goblets in toast, utterly unbothered. The table groans with grapes, bread loaves, a whole roast boar, and an overturned chalice spilling wine. A lute player sits in the corner, a dog gnaws a bone beneath the table. Dramatic chiaroscuro lighting from a single iron candelabra and a tall window, deep shadows pooling in the corners. Painted in rich earth tones with cracked-varnish texture, visible brushwork in the manner of Bruegel. The warm, low-light rendering and fine grain of Kodak Portra 800 push-processed, soft golden highlights. Opulent, anachronistic, absurdly solemn."
